Canadian Bacon Studios

Blocky Stairs (WIP)

Summary:
2D Pixel Art Platformer based on climbing as many stairs as possible in one direction. 
As you climb the camera will move with you towards the right, but not to the left. 
Simple enemies will push you back, touching the left side of the screen will result in a game over.

Mechanics & Rules:

2D
Pixel Art
Controllable Jump
Infinite Run
Screen goes to the right, returning is the end condition.
Points based on amount of stairs jumped
Basic Enemies push you.
